# TypeScript

## Compiler settings (`tsconfig.app.json`)

- `verbatimModuleSyntax: true` тАФ use `import type` for type-only imports.
- `noUnusedLocals` / `noUnusedParameters` тАФ remove dead code; prefix with `_` only when required by an interface.
- `erasableSyntaxOnly: true` тАФ no `enum`; use string unions or `as const` objects.
- `noEmit: true` тАФ Vite handles bundling; `npm run build` runs `tsc -b` for type-checking.

## Types

- Exchange DTOs live in `src/lib/bitunix/types.ts` and `src/lib/binance/types.ts`.
- Feature-specific types co-locate with the module (`engine.ts` exports `TradePlan`, `SetupResult`, etc.).
- Re-export public types from orchestrator modules (`export type { X } from './signal'`).
- Prefer `interface` for object shapes that may be extended; `type` for unions and computed types.
- Use `LONG | 'SHORT'` string unions consistently for position direction.

## Modules

- Pure functions for indicators (`src/lib/indicators.ts`), candles (`src/lib/candles.ts`), scoring тАФ no React imports in `lib/`.
- Side-effect-free analysis in `src/features/analysis/setup/` тАФ testable without DOM.
- Async helpers: `src/lib/async.ts` for debounce/throttle patterns.

## Errors

- `BitunixError` in `rest.ts` carries `code`; surface user-readable messages in UI.
- Don't swallow errors silently тАФ show inline error state or toast-style message in the panel.

## Naming

- Hooks: `use` prefix (`useCandles`, `useStats`, `usePositionReviews`).
- Stores: `useXxx` from Zustand (`useCredentials`, `useFavourites`).
- Files: camelCase for utilities (`entryQuality.ts`), PascalCase for components (`OrderTicket.tsx`).
